ywBDSW4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"> 『<a href="https://cover.lnk.to/Whatanamazingswing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">多么惊人的一击</a>』</figcaption></figure><figure class="wp-block-table is-style-stripes"><table><tbody><tr><td>歌词</td><td>TOPHAMHAT-KYO（假货型）</td></tr><tr><td>作品</td><td>假货类型。</td></tr><tr><td>安排</td><td>岩崎染料（假货型）</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h3 id="outline__1_4" class="wp-block-heading"> CD奖金</h3><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ADCreHezCWkNG-Pbsc-w-_7TAD-SM3gqQfGOYDE-3OWQF2CmgjlGXtmnYrwBCRPzwizF-lJbnAblPK7Z4glPzAghT0ADP7boGWTx7Ltnwq7n2VpxJRwVezln7bJu0GtETfiRIbhGYWjufL_5lFPAGRtom9o6=w1097-h617-s-no-gm" alt=""/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿 © 2016 COVER Corp. </figcaption></figure><p></p><div class="zgule65480af211d23" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
